b2b.sh:
  BLAST to BIM

Usage:
  SCRIPT --inp INP --out OUT

Mandatory Parameters:
  -i|--inp INP: the format 4 BLAST result, missing means reading from standard input.
  see "dat/test/m2r_Aox2.o4" for an example.

Optional  Parameters:

  --out: output filename, adds ".bim" to it if the surfix is missing; infer from INP
  if unspecified
